classifiers: Topic :: Software Development :: Libraries :: Python Modules
info.description:
Introduction
============

This package adds ``paster create`` like functionality to the django
``manage.py`` command.

The full documentation can be found at http://dja-skel.rtfd.org

The project is hosted at http://code.google.com/p/dja-skel/

Changelog
=========

0.1 - Unreleased
----------------

* pre-alpha release in order to gather somo external testing, opinions
  and so on.
